{"tid":2329259,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偷信換卡晶片盜款 男子被捕","createTime":"2020-12-17T06:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T07:07:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b71fe422b24a1f67c532a47c5a96719750b90377","tid":2329259,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/HZOGSPFSYFFO5IXIXO2NTQSJ44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FHZOGSPFSYFFO5IXIXO2NTQSJ44%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28eEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=d2866bf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FHZOGSPFSYFFO5IXIXO2NTQSJ44%2F&h=cf831b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/HZOGSPFSYFFO5IXIXO2NTQSJ44/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n偷信換卡晶片盜款 男子被捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方揭發有偷信賊將信用卡晶片偷龍轉鳳，令受害人無遺失信用卡下，仍被人盜款 ；一名男子前日被捕。賊人在保安措施較差的屋邨偷取銀行信件，更換新信用卡上的晶片，再將信用卡放回信封「物歸原主」，待持卡人啟動信用卡後，即使用套上真晶片的假卡，在櫃員機提取現金。警方去年5月至今年11月，共接獲14宗舉報，總損失32萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，賊人針對深水埗及紅磡區多處保安措施較差，或信箱較隱蔽的住宅大廈，<span class=\"orange\">偷去信箱內由銀行或財務機構發出的新信用卡，以及載有信用卡密碼的信件，賊人以工具移除信用卡晶片，再裝入假卡；又以另一張假晶片裝回卡主的信用卡上，放入信封，再放回信箱內。卡主收信後如常確認信用卡，賊人便到櫃員機作現金透支，卡主獲銀行通知，始獲悉信用卡被盜用透支。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fqc40OcNBob2hvmdQZxCAAV3ggI=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IBPWFPFCHVH23NKOQXQBYIITWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFqc40OcNBob2hvmdQZxCAAV3ggI%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIBPWFPFCHVH23NKOQXQBYIITWA.jpg&h=89c2c726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方在被捕男子寓所撿獲多張信用卡晶片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警接14宗舉報 涉款32萬<br />\n<br />\n早前警方接獲14宗舉報，涉款32萬元，調查後鎖定一名49歲男子，前日5時許該男子在牛頭角道提款機以假卡提取現金後，遭埋伏探員以涉盜竊及偽造文書罪名當場拘捕。有人承認與多宗同類案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方在被捕男子寓所搜出28張晶片，相信由不同銀行卡移除，並撿獲不同的銀行卡、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方提醒各。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MyuKlt4dIL2Vfw4U58OEb4c2SZk=/638x227/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DXC4AFJYJZBN3NXRHRTXLQOEUA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMyuKlt4dIL2Vfw4U58OEb4c2SZk%3D%2F638x227%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDXC4AFJYJZBN3NXRHRTXLQOEUA.gif&h=979e30f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a34ae16277eac686dfbb6461dfba43903ded6214","tid":2329259,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"都幾高明"},{"pid":"4c61a1175b3422d593edada180a1762cae14174b","tid":2329259,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:18:08.000Z","msg":"呢個堅犀利"},{"pid":"9d8f620b6d76e87ee83fdd29177ce49603ab0acc","tid":2329259,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"條友懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\non79 點會無人發現<br />\n<br />\n點會捉唔到你<br />\n<br />\n香港全街都有cctv 無完美犯罪架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a9fab8221edd64b41aca89eac39e5ccf81f3e8","tid":2329259,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"catch me if you can"},{"pid":"2b709f0cc8ca6f3173f7532b0b360f92329f55c4","tid":2329259,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"啲看更真係同隱形人冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886d32e6cf5e627d6e05ce8790d09c4a5fa0be35","tid":2329259,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8f620b6d76e87ee83fdd29177ce49603ab0acc","tid":2329259,"uid":8014,"like":1,"d